name: Baby Girl Zibra/Pink Flower Beanie Hat
description:
This hat is the perfect accessory for your little princess! You will receive one black crochet style hat in newborn infant size. They hats are perfect for ages birth through 12 months. You will also receive one Zibra/Pink Flower Clip.The flower is attached to a double prong alligator with White grosgrain ribbon.

Attach the flower clip to the hat, wear the hat alone or wear the flower clip in your hair! Three looks in one!
